# Shopware Frontends (Headless)

## When relevant
- Only for **custom storefronts** (e.g. Vue/Nuxt, React, Astro) instead of the classic Shopware storefront.
- Reference: https://developer.shopware.com/frontends/

## Concepts
- **Composable Frontends:** platform-agnostic custom storefronts; demo with Vue.js/Nuxt 3.
- Store API for products, cart, checkout, CMS; composables (e.g. useCart, useProduct, useCheckout).
- Templates: Vue Starter, Blank, Demo Store, Custom Vue/React/Astro.

## Template / your project
- Default is the **classic storefront** (Twig/SCSS/JS in theme plugin). Use Frontends docs only when a headless frontend is planned or present.
